name: Borderland Crispbread
desc: Crispbread made from rye flour. The pattern on the crispbread is created by pressing Icy Pebbles into it, while it's said that the hole in its center is also made in imitation of such. It contains barely any moisture, making it well-suited to long storage.

value.text: Increases all party members' DEF by 107 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
